name: SHILP SADHANA
briefDescription: SHILP SADHANA is a society, established in the year 1984, registered with The Registrar, Firms Societies & Chits, Uttar Pradesh, under Societies Registration Act 26, of 1860 with Registration No. 768/84-85.Since last 28 years we have provide support to more than 1000 artisans of handicraft sector mostly women.
